{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2045, "height": 2772, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "我是它众多名字当中的一个。\n我的体内众语喧哗，\n延缓着祖先的习惯；\n同样的习惯还将长存于\n\n我的尚未得见的子孙。\n\n或许一个伟大的人物\n\n曾在他的时代声名远播；\n现在他是一个符号，\n一捧无处可寻的尘土，\n一段无人记起的旧闻。\n\n家谱中的阴影\n\n是卑微的陈氏，张氏，葛氏，\n无人眷念的女性，和母亲。\n\n而今，这份我祖父亲手写下的\n郑重托付给我的《杜氏家谱》\n向我要求着那不容置疑的更新—\n那不断重复的生命之链中的一环。\n2002.1.26\n", "block_bbox": [288, 245, 978, 1398], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "源于杜姓的姓氏", "block_bbox": [706, 1547, 1207, 1614], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "一、先居", "block_bbox": [209, 1701, 434, 1748], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "先氏源于出自杜姓，以祖名为氏。相传周大夫杜伯的儿子在晋国作官，被封在先邑，他的子孙于是有以邑为姓，称为先姓。晋文公提拔他的后人先轸为中军元帅，职掌国政。先轸曾经率领晋军在崤山一带打败秦军，他的儿子先且居后来继位中军元帅，在彭衙再一次打败秦军。先且居的子孙有以他的名字中的“居”字作为姓氏的，称为居氏，世代相传。居氏得姓始祖先且居。居氏源出于先氏。春秋时期，晋国的先轸和先且居父子曾先后担任晋国的中军元帅。分别在崤山和彭衙打败了奏军。为晋国立下赫赫战功。先且居的子孙因祖上的业绩而感荣耀，便以他的名字为姓氏，称为居氏。故居氏的得姓始祖就是先且居。\n", "block_bbox": [202, 1767, 1698, 2353], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "二、范士", "block_bbox": [207, 2366, 431, 2418], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "以邑为氏，据《元和姓纂》及《通志·氏族略》载，帝尧裔孙刘累之后，在", "block_bbox": [291, 2431, 1694, 2482], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1815, 737, 1892, 1434], "block_id": 6, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "四一八", "block_bbox": [1816, 2088, 1869, 2209], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 7}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9677891731262207, "coordinate": [202.0751953125, 1767.42822265625, 1698.9530029296875, 2353.52880859375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8649364709854126, "coordinate": [288.4493408203125, 245.79730224609375, 978.6273193359375, 1398.045654296875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8638522028923035, "coordinate": [209.3607635498047, 1701.6688232421875, 434.66986083984375, 1748.1080322265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.837466835975647, "coordinate": [291.7598876953125, 2431.41015625, 1694.9100341796875, 2482.0302734375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8212687373161316, "coordinate": [207.00384521484375, 2366.822265625, 431.01141357421875, 2418.419921875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7263683080673218, "coordinate": [706.3360595703125, 1547.2991943359375, 1207.41162109375, 1614.4664306640625]}, {"cls_id": 18, "label": "aside_text", "score": 0.5705534815788269, "coordinate": [1815.4591064453125, 737.4684448242188, 1892.3011474609375, 1434.413818359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.48376014828681946, "coordinate": [1816.18115234375, 2088.956298828125, 1869.98291015625, 2209.779052734375]}]}, "overall_ocr_res": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[301, 246], [840, 248], [840, 296], [301, 294]], [[301, 312], [664, 314], [664, 362], [300, 359]], [[299, 377], [665, 379], [665, 427], [298, 425]], [[301, 444], [731, 444], [731, 491], [301, 491]], [[299, 512], [704, 510], [704, 555], [300, 557]], [[298, 577], [685, 574], [685, 622], [299, 624]], [[301, 642], [747, 637], [747, 685], [302, 690]], [[301, 709], [659, 709], [659, 754], [301, 754]], [[1798, 721], [1910, 721], [1910, 1010], [1798, 1010]], [[299, 771], [702, 773], [702, 821], [298, 818]], [[300, 837], [702, 839], [702, 883], [299, 881]], [[302, 903]