59], [975, 1401], [802, 1401]], [[709, 1546], [1206, 1549], [1206, 1618], [709, 1615]], [[211, 1702], [437, 1697], [438, 1750], [212, 1755]], [[299, 1763], [1698, 1773], [1697, 1824], [298, 1814]], [[211, 1830], [1697, 1838], [1696, 1888], [211, 1880]], [[214, 1896], [1696, 1903], [1695, 1953], [214, 1946]], [[212, 1963], [1695, 1968], [1694, 2017], [212, 2013]], [[212, 2030], [1696, 2033], [1695, 2084], [212, 2081]], [[1812, 2084], [1876, 2084], [1876, 2215], [1812, 2215]], [[213, 2097], [1694, 2097], [1694, 2150], [213, 2150]], [[211, 2167], [1694, 2165], [1695, 2215], [211, 2217]], [[210, 2235], [1695, 2230], [1696, 2281], [210, 2286]], [[205, 2299], [287, 2299], [287, 2361], [205, 2361]], [[206, 2368], [433, 2363], [434, 2419], [207, 2424]], [[297, 2436], [1695, 2429], [1696, 2480], [298, 2486]]], "rec_boxes": [[301, 246, 840, 296], [300, 312, 664, 362], [298, 377, 665, 427], [301, 444, 731, 491], [299, 510, 704, 557], [298, 574, 685, 624], [301, 637, 747, 690], [301, 709, 659, 754], [1798, 721, 1910, 1010], [298, 771, 702, 821], [299, 837, 702, 883], [302, 903, 557, 948], [299, 965, 827, 1016], [303, 1035, 787, 1078], [1809, 1029, 1900, 1441], [300, 1094, 851, 1146], [300, 1161, 832, 1211], [304, 1228, 933, 1274], [300, 1292, 911, 1339], [802, 1359, 975, 1401], [709, 1546, 1206, 1618], [211, 1697, 438, 1755], [298, 1763, 1698, 1824], [211, 1830, 1697, 1888], [214, 1896, 1696, 1953], [212, 1963, 1695, 2017], [212, 2030, 1696, 2084], [1812, 2084, 1876, 2215], [213, 2097, 1694, 2150], [211, 2165, 1695, 2217], [210, 2230, 1696, 2286], [205, 2299, 287, 2361], [206, 2363, 434, 2424], [297, 2429, 1696, 2486]]}}, "markdown": {"text": "我是它众多名字当中的一个。\n\n我的体内众语喧哗，\n\n延缓着祖先的习惯；\n\n同样的习惯还将长存于\n\n我的尚未得见的子孙。\n\n或许一个伟大的人物\n\n曾在他的时代声名远播；\n\n现在他是一个符号，\n\n一捧无处可寻的尘土，\n\n一段无人记起的旧闻。\n\n家谱中的阴影\n\n是卑微的陈氏，张氏，葛氏，\n\n无人眷念的女性，和母亲。\n\n而今，这份我祖父亲手写下的\n\n郑重托付给我的《杜氏家谱》\n\n向我要求着那不容置疑的更新—\n\n那不断重复的生命之链中的一环。\n\n2002.1.26\n\n\n\n## 源于杜姓的姓氏\n\n## 一、 先居\n\n先氏源于出自杜姓，以祖名为氏。相传周大夫杜伯的儿子在晋国作官，被封在先邑，他的子孙于是有以邑为姓，称为先姓。晋文公提拔他的后人先轸为中军元帅，职掌国政。先轸曾经率领晋军在崤山一带打败秦军，他的儿子先且居后来继位中军元帅，在彭衙再一次打败秦军。先且居的子孙有以他的名字中的“居”字作为姓氏的，称为居氏，世代相传。居氏得姓始祖先且居。居氏源出于先氏。春秋时期，晋国的先轸和先且居父子曾先后担任晋国的中军元帅。分别在崤山和彭衙打败了奏军。为晋国立下赫赫战功。先且居的子孙因祖上的业绩而感荣耀，便以他的名字为姓氏，称为居氏。故居氏的得姓始祖就是先且居。\n\n\n\n## 二、 范士\n\n以邑为氏，据《元和姓纂》及《通志·氏族略》载，帝尧裔孙刘累之后，在\n\n四一八", "isStart": true, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//a1efd7cc-83f8-4523-aaf9-fc9dc27c6d72/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A38%3A33Z%2F-1%2F%2Fa00c2e28e97439e14d375509f38a5846474c10e04096202d5ce79d02244dfa65", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//a1efd7cc-83f8-4523-aaf9-fc9dc27c6d72/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A38%3A33Z%2F-1%2F%2F67a9e635b6487ac43f400d8c4399d1d4e8a6639cc6ccd1d2b5d461c7872a05a8", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//a1efd7cc-83f8-4523-aaf9-fc9dc27c6d72/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A38%3A33Z%2F-1%2F%2F458eae77e53e49f5fb2e7d1f348767d14a3ef76f37ba05149d52e709bf16a854", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//a1efd7cc-83f8-4523-aaf9-fc9dc27c6d72/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A38%3A33Z%2F-1%2F%2Ffcccb6a7650dc4911ccfab7150f8ffcd814055daced646247048b945a3fbf6b0"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//a1efd7cc-83f8-4523-aaf9-fc9dc27c6d72/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A38%3A32Z%2F-1%2F%2Fb6bb8c244f32dc288e6cc302111d8288bea2cd641f98ed648b1264d6c8fe7bfd"}], "dataInfo": {"width": 2045, "height": 2772, 